CLAUDE.md

# Manifest.toml is Julia-version-specific (stdlib UUIDs and JLL
# resolution differ between minor versions). Don't ship it — let
# `Pkg.instantiate()` resolve fresh from Project.toml [compat] on
# each user's / CI job's Julia version. Matches the standard Julia
# package convention for non-application repos.
Manifest.toml

# Pre-computed reconstructions are NOT shipped (~40 MB, regenerable
# via `make -k all`). The pre-rendered PNGs in data/ stay in the repo
# so the data/README.md gallery and the top-level abstract figure
# render on GitHub without cloning.
data/*_h.csv.gz

.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

*.swp
*.swo
*~
